@startuml Sequence – CLI Interaction
title TradingAgents — CLI User Interaction Flow

skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

actor "User\n(Terminal)" as USER
participant "cli/main.py\n(Typer App)" as CLI
participant "MessageBuffer\n(event tracker)" as BUF
participant "StatsCallbackHandler\n(LangChain callback)" as STATS
participant "TradingAgentsGraph" as TAG
participant "Rich Console\n(live output)" as RICH

USER -> CLI : ta run --ticker AAPL --date 2025-01-10

CLI -> CLI : Load/validate config\n(prompt if missing API keys)
CLI -> CLI : Build analyst_selection\nfrom CLI flags

CLI -> RICH : Display banner & config summary

CLI -> BUF : MessageBuffer()
CLI -> STATS : StatsCallbackHandler()

CLI -> TAG : TradingAgentsGraph(config)
TAG --> CLI : graph instance

CLI -> RICH : Display "Starting analysis..."

CLI -> TAG : propagate(\n  ticker="AAPL",\n  date="2025-01-10",\n  callbacks=[STATS]\n)

loop For each LangGraph event streamed
  TAG --> BUF : on_agent_start(agent_name, state)
  BUF -> RICH : Print agent header\n"[Market Analyst] Running..."

  TAG --> BUF : on_tool_start(tool_name, inputs)
  BUF -> RICH : Print tool call\n"  → get_stock_data(AAPL, 2025-01-10)"

  TAG --> BUF : on_tool_end(tool_name, output)
  BUF -> RICH : Print tool result summary\n"  ← 252 rows fetched"

  TAG --> BUF : on_agent_finish(agent_name, output)
  BUF -> RICH : Print report excerpt
end

TAG --> CLI : (final_state, signal_dict)

CLI -> STATS : get_summary()
STATS --> CLI : {llm_calls: 18, tool_calls: 12, tokens: 45320}

CLI -> RICH : Display final decision\n┌─────────────────────────┐\n│ Signal: BUY             │\n│ Rating: Buy             │\n│ Price Target: $205      │\n└─────────────────────────┘

CLI -> RICH : Display stats summary\n"LLM calls: 18 | Tokens: 45.3K | Time: 4m 22s"

CLI -> RICH : Display saved results path\n"Results saved to: results/AAPL_2025-01-10.json"

CLI --> USER : Exit 0

@enduml
